					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>This inscription records a gift of gold for perpetual lamp to the temple of Śrī Pōndaip-perumāṉaḍigaḷ by Naṟṟuḻāṉ Nakkerumāṉ, native of Ilaṅkāḍu in Veṇkkuṉṟakkōṭṭam. The <hi rend="italic">gaṇapperumakkaḷ</hi> were entrusted with the responsibility of carrying out this charity.</p>						

						</summary>
